---
description: Save tokens and avoid risky changes
alwaysApply: true
---

Before editing:
- confirm project folder, git remote, and branch
- inspect only relevant files
- make small diffs
- avoid reading unrelated folders
- do not rewrite whole files unless necessary
- do not use GitHub unless it helps the task

For this project:
- this is ONIS Web
- allowed GitHub repo: onis-labs/onis-web
- do not touch PathBuild
- do not touch onis-ios unless explicitly asked

When changing web UI:
- use shared design tokens
- avoid random inline colors
- avoid random padding
- spacing must be divisible by 4 or 8
- keep font sizes minimal
- do not touch deployment settings
- do not touch production environment variables

Never touch:
- API keys
- .env files
- auth
- payments
- database schema
- git remotes
- production data
- deployment settings

Never commit, push, create PRs, or create issues unless explicitly approved.
